Description: SecuBox Matrix Synapse - Federated Chat Server
 LXC-based Matrix Synapse homeserver for SecuBox.
 Provides federated, encrypted messaging with Element web client support.
 .
 Features:
  - Full Matrix Synapse homeserver in LXC container
  - User and room management via web UI
  - Bridge support (Telegram, Discord, Signal, etc.)
  - Element web client installation
  - Federation support
  - Backup/restore functionality
